sentences: James Stanley McCarty (born 25 July 1943) is an English musician, best known as the drummer for the Yardbirds and Renaissance.
Following Chris Dreja's departure from the Yardbirds in 2013, McCarty became the only member of the band to feature in every line up.
Since 1992 he has been playing with the reformed Yardbirds.
